{"tid":1890492,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony期望未來能與Marvel繼續合作拍《蜘蛛俠》","createTime":"2020-02-21T08:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T11:29:36.000Z","uid":105567,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5cda2201e86dc84763cb9050cf4bd52eca490018","tid":1890492,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:24:23.000Z","msg":"上年8月Marvel與Sony在《蜘蛛俠》電影共同融資協議上出現分歧，令蜘蛛俠要離開MCU，幸好主角湯賀蘭力挽狂瀾，化解兩間公司的矛盾，讓Marvel能製作多一部《蜘蛛俠》個人電影，而蜘蛛俠亦可繼續現身在MCU作品之中。<br />\n經過虛驚一場後，Sony影視娛樂Tom Rothman近日再派定心丸，當被問及與Marvel的合作夥伴關係能否繼續時，Rothman回覆希望合作可延續下去，他形容這次的合作是三贏，不論是Sony、Marvel及廣大的fans都是一場勝利。<br />\n資料來源: ComicBookMovie<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/mobile/article.aspx?id=30114&amp;catid=35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Fmobile%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D30114%26catid%3D35&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=968892a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgolden.com/mobile/article.aspx?id=30114&amp;catid=35</a>"},{"pid":"a286e9b84f911fce2ba694550d385fcb7dc8aca5","tid":1890492,"uid":151333,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笠水"},{"pid":"60a16ab372410d558eb3be166ca0fef413516a48","tid":1890492,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a286e9b84f911fce2ba694550d385fcb7dc8aca5","tid":1890492,"uid":151333,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笠水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:00:28.000Z","msg":"上次係Sony say no 咩？"},{"pid":"27dadfee3fef24b449a2bef5a7b601ebcf446517","tid":1890492,"uid":64922,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60a16ab372410d558eb3be166ca0fef413516a48","tid":1890492,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a286e9b84f911fce2ba694550d385fcb7dc8aca5","tid":1890492,"uid":151333,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笠水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:00:28.000Z","msg":"上次係Sony say no 咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:28:34.000Z","msg":"依家基本係未到新約只係理行埋第一份約<br />\n蜘蛛俠新3部曲第3集<br />\n但睇勢sony自家拍多幾套獨立蜘蛛俠宇宙其他歹、英角色後<br />\n就會要荷蘭仔主力過返來拍蜘蛛俠宇宙<br />\nmarvel都知sony唔會順灘去無了期任用蜘蛛俠<br />\nmarvel未來亦都唔會再用蜘蛛俠來做重心hero架喇<br />\n未來主力都係谷返xmen &amp; f4<br />\n我9估拍完下集後蜘蛛俠係mcu宇宙散band機會極大"},{"pid":"35f9942b87badbf0c0d976baaa592ae229e5c282","tid":1890492,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"屌，攬炒失敗"}]}